functions.docstring:
Embed the event text once (Gemini). For each label, compare to its exemplars and
return the top cosine similarity (0..1) plus a short rationale.

Returns shape:
  {
    "<label>": {
      "score": float,
      "reason": str,
      "skipped": bool
    },
    ...
  }

Pull transcript and verdict from the graph.
Returns:
  {
    'transcript': [{'turn': int, 'role': str, 'content': str}, ...],
    'verdict': {'outcome': str, 'confidence': float, 'uncertainty': float}
  }

